"Tax Identity Theft Prevention Week, National: January 25-29",United States,1,25,2021,1,29,2021,18,42,46,52,,,Weekly,Changes,Last Monday in January for 5 days,https://www.identitytheft.gov,Tax_ID_Theft_WeekF.jpg,Tax_ID_Theft_WeekE.jpg,About Tax Identity Theft Prevention Week,,"Beginning in 2014 the Federal Trade Commission has launched an awareness campaign under the title National Tax Identity Theft Prevention Week. 

Tax identity theft happens when someone uses your Social Security number to get a tax refund or a job. 

